Config/Abstract/Ini version 0.10
================================

Config::Abstract::Ini is the implementation of Config::Abstract for
.ini-style files. To make it compatible with other file formats, we
support a few extensions to the  .ini format, most notably  nesting
if sections by using double colons as delimiters in  section names.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Config::Abstract

